Bright- water seems greener but still clear

High sun- calm- algae bloom underway

Rain daily from 6/18 to 6/21- sunny- light chop.  Lake level: very high

Rainy- windy- no floating algae- lake highest in 8-10 years
Fishing and swimming great- over 2" of rain in the last 24 hours
Sunny the last 4 days- 90 F+- 1.5" rain on sat.- some floating mats of filamentous green or blue-green algae

Lots of rain- sunny day- no chop

Pollen bloom continues.  Suspended photo plankton obviously developing in the lake.

Sunny + calm. larger "globs" of algae. water is clearer.
